Absolutely the worst buffet ever . The food here sucks ASS !!!!! I have been to many casino buffets and this is by far . Straight shitty ! It might have been an off night .
However I tried a little of everything and nothing was remotely palatable!  Oh well gave it a try and that's all I can  say.  Buyer beware  !!!!
And yes I stayed at the Bellagio for 4 nights during this trip . Great place . The Buffet Sucks Balls .